  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;近日，汉阳城管部门采取&ldquo;文明接力&rdquo;的方式对违规行人进行处罚，即如市容监督员发现行人闯红灯过马路，该行人就必须在原地替市容监督员&ldquo;值班&rdquo;，提醒市民看灯通行，直到抓到下一个违规过马路的行人才可&ldquo;下岗&rdquo;。据悉，该方法实行一周以来，违规行人较此前下降五成。<br />\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;据介绍，此前为了保证行人安全，城管部门安排市容监督员值守在主干道路口。根据有关管理规定，市容监督员可对违规行人处以罚款，但不少行人对此抵触情绪很大，没有起到宣传教育效果。而&ldquo;文明接力&rdquo;的方式让人更易接受。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tChinese way of walking across the road is well known at home and abroad. And it poses great threat to both pedestrians themselves and car drivers. After the measure of fine does not work well, another measure comes out. That is to say, when one person is caught crossing the road in a wrong way, he or she cannot leave until another person who breaks the rule appears. This measure, which is called civilization&rsquo;s passing on by someone, in a way works well. However, this kind of civilization&rsquo;s passing on makes no sense. It is not only a matter of safety but also a matter of civilization. This kind of civilization definitely should not be promoted to pass on. Then what kind of civilization should be passed on? The answer just lies in everyone&rsquo;s heart. The only we need to do is to take action right now.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWe Chinese have always been criticized of uncivilized behaviors nationwide, involving spitting, talking loudly in public places and running the red light. Particularly, when pedestrians walk cross the road, they tend to go through the red light, taking granted that no cars dare run into them. In response to the misunderstanding, local governments have carried out various measures. The most effective way is to let citizens themselves be the supervisor &ndash; finding people who are walking through red light. It is said that the number of people running the red light decreased by half in one week. Nevertheless, people doubt about the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/legitimacy\" target=\"_blank\">legitimacy</a> of this action. The related department has no right to restrict personal liberty. In this way, I suppose we can take a flexible measure, to let pedestrians be the supervisor or pay fines instead.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/919226/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p621004/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p621004\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p620245/\">不得不看的几部美剧：经典+新作</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p621114/\">亚马逊发布首款智能手机Fire Phone</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p620987/\">李克强出访英国秀英文 获卡梅伦称赞</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"h